    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for someone looking for utility over aesthetics. The exterior shows visible signs of age, including some fading paint on the hood and a few noticeable scratches and minor dings along the side panels. Inside, the upholstery has some wear and a small tear on the driver's seat, though all essential electronics and the air conditioning remain functional. It has been regularly serviced, but prospective buyers should expect some upcoming minor maintenance typical for a car of this age and mileage.",
