    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone looking for a budget-friendly option. While it runs and drives well, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the clear coat in certain areas. Inside, the upholstery shows typical wear and tear from regular use, including some staining and a few small tears in the fabric. Mechanically, the car has been maintained with regular oil changes, though it may require some minor suspension work in the near future. It\u2019s an honest, high-mileage car that still has plenty of life left for a practical owner.",
      "price": 21000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
